{
  "stem": "12455.1",
  "chunk_idx": 4,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 3.9,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 78,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "I was scared to go out.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 78,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "I was scared to move.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 78,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "I was scared to do anything.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 79,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "And then I had to go outside.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 79,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "When I go out, I was hiding in hot houses and abandoned houses.",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 79,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "During that time, the Ukrainian police that was working with the Germans and the Nazis, they were searching the town for-- for Jews that was left over.",
      "word_count": 27
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 79,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "And two times, they caught me.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 79,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "And they put me in jail.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 79,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "And during the day, they would round up women and children and put everybody in one cell. 5 o'clock in the evening, they would let us out to the woods.",
      "word_count": 30
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 79,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "And they had a grave dug.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 79,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "And they would kill everybody.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 79,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 8,
      "text": "And I managed to run away both times.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 80,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "I was-- easing off-- we were led in the woods.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 80,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "And there was guards on the side and in the back.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 80,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "But I was easing off to the side, and easing off to the side, and just took off and ran.",
      "word_count": 20
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 80,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "And either they saw it and didn't see it.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 80,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "Or, they didn't see me run away.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 81,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Right.",
      "word_count": 1
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 81,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "The last time that I ran away, I decided not to go back in town, because it's-- I would have been killed too.",
      "word_count": 23
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 81,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "So I decided to walk-- I was scared of the front line.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 81,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "So I decided to walk to Poland.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 82,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "So I sat down, and I made up of facticious ID, ID with a Ukrainian or Russian name.",
      "word_count": 18
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 82,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "And I put it in my pocket.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 82,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "And I just walked so many miles every day until it got dark.",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 82,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "And then I would come to a village and beg for bread, beg for food, beg for a place to stay.",
      "word_count": 21
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 83,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "And if I didn't have a place to stay, I would sleep outside.",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 83,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "It led on.",
      "word_count": 3
    }
  ],
